incident_updates.body: We are continuing to work on a fix for this issue.

Start time : 17/08/2023 07:26 UTC Service impact : Latency is being observed on our backbone between Asia and USA Root cause : 2 fiber cuts caused the incident Ongoing actions : Our teams are currently in contact with our operator to resolve the incident.
